Transformations

Compile with make. It uses rustc, instead of cargo now, for building.

Includes:
* Scaling
* Translations
* Rotations
* Bezier Curves
* Hermite Curves
* Circle Drawing
* 3D Boxes
* 3D Spheres (currently minor vec flaw in fn add_sphere)
* 3D Toruses (also affected by minor vec flaw)
